      "sn": 4,
      "content": "a. General Information"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "section_title": null,
      "page": 1,
      "sn": 5,
      "content": "The active pharmaceutical ingredient is Solifenacin Succinate. It is a white to off-white crystalline powder. The"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "section_title": null,
      "page": 1,
      "sn": 6,
      "content": "chemical name is butanedioic acid, compounded with (1S)-1-phenyl-1,2,3,4-tetrahydroisoquinoline-2-carboxylic acid"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "section_title": null,
      "page": 1,
      "sn": 7,
      "content": "(1S,3R)-3-hydroxy-1-phenylpropyl ester, (1S)-1-phenyl-1,2,3,4-tetrahydroisoquinoline-2-carboxylic acid (1S,3R)-3-"
    },
    {
