      "section_title": null,
      "page": 4,
      "sn": 95,
      "content": "d. Reference Product Information"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "section_title": null,
      "page": 4,
      "sn": 96,
      "content": "The reference product is Solifenacin Succinate Tablets BP 5 mg, manufactured by Leben Life Sciences Pvt. Ltd. The"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "section_title": null,
      "page": 4,
      "sn": 97,
      "content": "product is a light yellow coloured, round shaped, film coated tablet containing 5 mg of Solifenacin Succinate. It is"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "section_title": null,
      "page": 4,
      "sn": 98,
      "content": "intended for oral administration and is packed in ALU/ALU blister packs of 10 tablets. The target product profile aims"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "section_title": null,
      "page": 4,
      "sn": 99,
      "content": "for a 36-month shelf life under controlled storage conditions, with specifications aligned to the British"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "section_title": null,
      "page": 4,
      "sn": 100,
      "content": "Pharmacopoeia."
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "section_title": null,
      "page": 4,
      "sn": 101,
      "content": "Confidential!"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "section_title": null,
      "page": 4,
      "sn": 102,
      "content": "Page 4"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "section_title": null,
